These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, tiparillo, baccarat, cain
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
3. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
5. the dannemann-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Cigar   | baccarat | cain      | dannemann | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, handball, badminton
1. the egyptian is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is badminton##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Sport           | handball      | lacrosse    | snowboarding | badminton      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing, rugby, rowing
1. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Sport   | sailing  | rowing   | rugby | water-polo    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
4 different games are played: bridge, go, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing go##2
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
5. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Game   | scrabble   | monopoly     | go    | bridge       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
City: prague, boston, san-francisco, marseilles
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| City   | boston  | marseilles | prague | san-francisco |

