.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, snake, goat
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
3. the owner of the goat is between the police-officer and the owner of the snake##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Pet   | snake        | goat     | pony       | hamster   |

