.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, hot-chocolate, 7up
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
5. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea | milk  | hot-chocolate  | 7up   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

