.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
House: colonial, victorian, craftsman, tower
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the victorian house is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| House   | victorian     | tower | craftsman     | colonial   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

