2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | puzzles | drawing | baking   | chess |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

