.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, bellflower, begonia
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
5. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Flower      | poppy  | begonia | daisy | bellflower |

