1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
5. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| Flower   | orchid     | balloon-flower | begonia  | iris |

