.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, baking, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
6. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks   | baking  | collecting      | reading       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

