The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, d&b, ambient
1. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of disco##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of disco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | ambient  | r&b | disco        |

