.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, reggae, jazz, funk
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | funk | reggae      | country        |

 